<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1" />
  <title>Inventory Control System - Home</title>
  <link href="http://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Poppins:wght@400;600&display=swap" rel="stylesheet" />
  <style>
    * { margin: 0; padding: 0; box-sizing: border-box; }
    body {
      font-family: 'Poppins', sans-serif;
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, #6a11cb, #2575fc);
      color: #fff;
      min-height: 100vh;
      display: flex;
      flex-direction: column;
      animation: fadeIn 1s ease forwards;
    }
    @keyframes fadeIn { from {opacity: 0;} to {opacity: 1;} }

    nav {
      background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1);
      backdrop-filter: blur(10px);
      padding: 1rem 2rem;
      display: flex;
      justify-content: space-between;
      align-items: center;
      box-shadow: 0 3px 10px rgba(0,0,0,0.2);
    }
    nav h2 { font-weight: 600; font-size: 1.4rem; letter-spacing: 1px; }
    nav a {
      color: white;
      text-decoration: none;
      font-weight: 500;
      margin-left: 1.5rem;
      transition: color 0.3s ease;
    }
    nav a:hover { color: #00e6f6; }

    header {
      text-align: center;
      padding: 2rem;
      margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
    }
    header h1 {
      font-size: 2.5rem;
      margin-bottom: 0.8rem;
    }
    header p {
      font-size: 1.2rem;
      max-width: 750px;
      margin: 0 auto;
      opacity: 0.9;
    }

    main {
      max-width: 1100px;
      width: 90%;
      margin: auto;
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(280px, 1fr));
      gap: 2rem;
      padding-bottom: 3rem;
    }
    .card {
      background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.12);
      backdrop-filter: blur(8px);
      border-radius: 15px;
      padding: 2rem 1.5rem;
      box-shadow: 0 8px 20px rgba(0,0,0,0.2);
      text-align: center;
      transition: transform 0.3s ease, box-shadow 0.3s ease;
      cursor: pointer;
      color: #fff;
    }
    .card:hover { transform: translateY(-8px); box-shadow: 0 15px 35px rgba(0,0,0,0.3); }

    .card h3 {
      color: #38f9d7;
      margin-bottom: 1rem;
      font-size: 1.4rem;
      font-weight: 700;
    }
    .card p { font-size: 1rem; line-height: 1.5; margin-bottom: 1.5rem; opacity: 0.85; }

    .btn {
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, #43e97b, #38f9d7);
      color: white;
      padding: 0.7rem 1.3rem;
      border-radius: 8px;
      text-decoration: none;
      font-weight: 600;
      font-size: 1rem;
      transition: all 0.3s ease;
      display: inline-block;
    }
    .btn:hover { transform: scale(1.05); background: linear-gradient(135deg, #38f9d7, #43e97b); }

    footer {
      margin-top: auto;
      padding: 1rem;
      text-align: center;
      font-size: 0.9rem;
      opacity: 0.7;
      background: rgba(0,0,0,0.1);
    }

    @media (max-width: 480px) {
      header h1 { font-size: 2rem; }
      header p { font-size: 1rem; }
      nav h2 { font-size: 1.1rem; }
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>

  <nav>
    <h2>Inventory Dashboard</h2>
    <div>
      <!-- <a href="/">Home</a> -->
        <a href="/profile">Profile</a>
         <a href="/settings">Settings</a>
      <a href="/login">Logout</a>
    </div>
  </nav>

  <header>
    <h1>Welcome, <%= userName %> ðŸ‘‹</h1>
    <p>
      Track inventory in real-time, set reorder alerts, and manage your stock seamlessly with a single dashboard.
    </p>
  </header>

  <main>
    <div class="card" onclick="window.location.href='/add-item'">
      <h3>Add / Edit Inventory</h3>
      <p>Add or update items with SKU, type, measure unit, thresholds, and quantities.</p>
      <a href="/add-item" class="btn">Manage Inventory</a>
    </div>

    <div class="card" onclick="window.location.href='/inventory-list'">
      <h3>Inventory Overview</h3>
      <p>View stock levels, reserved items, and items that need reordering quickly.</p>
      <a href="/inventory-list" class="btn">View Inventory</a>
    </div>

    <div class="card" onclick="window.location.href='/transaction-log'">
      <h3>Transaction Log</h3>
      <p>See complete inflow & outflow history with timestamps and details.</p>
      <a href="/transaction-log" class="btn">View Log</a>
    </div>

    <div class="card" onclick="window.location.href='/alerts'">
      <h3>Reorder Alerts</h3>
      <p>Get alerts when stock levels drop below thresholds to avoid stock-outs.</p>
      <a href="/alerts" class="btn">Check Alerts</a>
    </div>

    <div class="card" onclick="window.location.href='/low-stock'">
      <h3>Low Stock Items</h3>
      <p>Check all items currently below their minimum stock threshold.</p>
      <a href="/low-stock" class="btn">View Low Stock</a>
    </div>

    <div class="card" onclick="window.location.href='/reserved-items'">
      <h3>Reserved Items</h3>
      <p>See which items are reserved for orders or production.</p>
      <a href="/reserved-items" class="btn">View Reserved</a>
    </div>

    <div class="card" onclick="window.location.href='/hazardous-materials'">
      <h3>Hazardous Materials</h3>
      <p>Track and manage items flagged as hazardous for compliance.</p>
      <a href="/hazardous-materials" class="btn">View Hazardous</a>
    </div>

    <div class="card" onclick="window.location.href='/items-available'">
      <h3>Inventory List</h3>
      <p>Manage items available for buying/selling with complete details.</p>
      <a href="/items-available" class="btn">Buy / Sell List</a>
    </div>
  </main>

  <footer>
    &copy; 2025 Inventory Control System. All rights reserved.
  </footer>

</body>
</html>
